{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>國際高級珠寶品牌卡地亞（Cartier）日前於香港半山私人府邸舉行「Cariter En Équilibre」高級珠寶展覽晚宴，古天樂、郭富城、劉嘉玲、林嘉欣、周興哲及炎明熹（Gigi）等都盛裝打扮出席，場面星光熠熠。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124846616101392384890634.jpeg/9DLQoijgEDchSl9wBx-uslQdo-j78mIUnaO5Sp2juUo\" alt=\"古天樂。（threads@kootinlok_louis）\"><figcaption>古天樂。（threads@kootinlok_louis）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124846613777616896274856.jpeg/KVVsHDmISUZimdoiDve9cuAPiPRbrEhm9gvjH_YL4x8\" alt=\"郭富城。（IG@aaronkwokxx）\"><figcaption>郭富城。（IG@aaronkwokxx）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124846611516755968512876.jpeg/KFFbdF9NyNJ7fyJB7w_8ZIPc4IC3AvwCP98HZT_fB2U\" alt=\"劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）\"><figcaption>劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124846609100705792617532.jpeg/0Oa8pmlLl1eJODcOBKxOMa9vzCP8t_-AWe2-rlntvq4\" alt=\"炎明熹、林嘉欣。（IG@yiminghay）\"><figcaption>炎明熹、林嘉欣。（IG@yiminghay）</figcaption></figure><p>劉嘉玲Deep V黑絲出席珠寶晚宴　與郭富城同框</p><p>活動當晚，郭富城同古天樂都西裝骨骨上陣，兩位型男佩戴高級腕錶，並在胸前別上造型胸針，盡顯成熟魅力。而劉嘉玲就以一身黑色Deep V高衩長裙亮相，戴上一套名貴珠寶，再披上粉紅色羽毛披肩，貴氣十足。劉嘉玲在IG分享了多張晚宴照片，當中包括與郭富城及周興哲的合照，氣場十足。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124846996889407488319486.jpeg/eDl5XfpXwXZe9PORYVTL5gqFRnJyoPni2JKZediSmXk\" alt=\"型！（threads@kootinlok_louis）\"><figcaption>型！（threads@kootinlok_louis）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124846994502717440943687.jpeg/P4gQuegO4p9-1O6hH_zUJ3K8MGioIn-1Bt-NHAbfjRw\" alt=\"型！（IG@aaronkwokxx）\"><figcaption>型！（IG@aaronkwokxx）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847015663505408749361.jpeg/b5VgiW4CnngLpYyx46AQsOYgsrFEmExYWh23e1odt3s\" alt=\"Deep V上陣！（IG@carinalau1208）\"><figcaption>Deep V上陣！（IG@carinalau1208）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847013281009664927130.jpeg/AbtM83denI2rnrJSmuwLhLLiu2tmK1BgBw2i6wcNous\" alt=\"貴氣十足！（IG@carinalau1208）\"><figcaption>貴氣十足！（IG@carinalau1208）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847010890125312498105.jpeg/FS4gKZuouZgVTBv3lewjLVSc7oYEx7og3bActd2wHLU\" alt=\"郭富城、劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）\"><figcaption>郭富城、劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847008415354880132048.jpeg/AcsZ5hMTAlZbTm7F8botFnpWv0kigMOJFHPolRRz6JU\" alt=\"周興哲、劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）\"><figcaption>周興哲、劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847006175465472960412.jpeg/iAKmC4D0E_I5Q7EoaszguAJEUT9-PZrJudTKxbnUysU\" alt=\"周興哲、劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）\"><figcaption>周興哲、劉嘉玲。（IG@carinalau1208）</figcaption></figure><p>炎明熹着吊帶裙成熟造型獲讚</p><p>而炎明熹（Gigi）獲邀在晚宴上獻唱，她一改昔日鄰家女孩形象，分別以黑色吊帶長裙及白色跌膊晚裝亮相，盡顯優雅成熟的一面，網民紛紛大讚她的造型甚具女人味，成功轉型！</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847334296260608645287.jpeg/xPG9D1EsXNmn1Kju75X4Q_bsr0JCUEFEEIglHhCIJR4\" alt=\"黑色吊帶長裙。（IG@yiminghay）\"><figcaption>黑色吊帶長裙。（IG@yiminghay）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847331804712960180234.jpeg/TK50OEnjZ9LONGz8u-w3Bfo_N_e6FsxT8AgCEfAIAhE\" alt=\"黑色吊帶長裙。（IG@yiminghay）\"><figcaption>黑色吊帶長裙。（IG@yiminghay）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847329409634304240381.jpeg/b40zIjkadD4bd9ixO93lMqvvDepgmbGplAmfFZQJnxU\" alt=\"白色跌膊晚裝。（IG@yiminghay）\"><figcaption>白色跌膊晚裝。（IG@yiminghay）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124847326788063232536027.jpeg/8Xj5iA29uyncJBut5IgdPHuRQGWiZuTk0RzRi9Ec0Ys\" alt=\"白色跌膊晚裝。（IG@yiminghay）\"><figcaption>白色跌膊晚裝。（IG@yiminghay）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T15:57:57.178446+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":730,"images":15,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}